WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Welcome to this lesson on vectors and kinematics.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Vectors describe both magnitude and direction in physical systems.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:20.000
We can break vectors into components to simplify analysis and calculations.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:27.000
In this session, we apply these ideas to motion and displacement.
